<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A fragment, ? from a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> front, very worn (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.55</measure> x <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.90</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face of the sarcophagus; there are designs—a circle and what looks like a shovel, below.</p>
</div>
